Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:13.30,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:15.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:18.78,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.32,0:00:22.88,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:26.59,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:30.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.32,0:00:33.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.85,0:00:36.51,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.49,0:00:40.17,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.05,0:00:44.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.70,0:00:48.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.27,0:00:50.92,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.92,0:00:54.66,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.48,0:00:59.13,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.13,0:01:02.78,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.33,0:01:10.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.81,0:01:12.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.89,0:01:14.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.71,0:01:18.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.81,0:01:24.73,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,140.389)}Cockroach Man!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.81,0:01:24.73,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(457.167,410.389)}The Dreadful
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.81,0:01:24.73,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(467.167,680.389)}Germ-Stuffed Ad Balloon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.82,0:01:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure I heard something...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.56,0:01:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.34,0:01:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.45,0:02:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.76,0:02:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't leave it here.\NClean it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.75,0:02:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That was pretty crummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.37,0:02:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, watch me work!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.00,0:02:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids aren't allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.91,0:02:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, that's no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.51,0:02:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, watch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.23,0:03:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't he great?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.56,0:03:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's handsome,\Nand he's also really talented!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.22,0:03:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.21,0:03:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.46,0:03:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.33,0:03:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.70,0:03:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.43,0:03:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.87,0:03:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You think Shocker's behind it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.85,0:03:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is why I didn't\Nwant to go bowling!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.55,0:03:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to tell Takeshi at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If Shocker is behind this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But why weren't the\Nrest of you affected?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd heard you'd gotten\Nobsessed with bowling,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but you even bought a ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,These are expensive,\Naren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.65,0:04:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Were the people who collapsed in the\Nbowling alley using their own balls?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,0:04:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't look like it, did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.91,0:04:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they used the\Nbowling alley's balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The test was a grand success.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Infecting the ball\Nholes with the bacteria
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.27,0:04:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,will let us rapidly\Nage the humans
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.51,0:04:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,without them ever\Nsuspecting a Shocker plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, use the strain with\Ngreater contagiousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,so that it will spread to those who\Ntouch the collapsed people as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If we cover cockroaches with\Nthe bacteria and disperse them,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the disease will spread like\Nwildfire and cause mass panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You think there's\Nbacteria in the holes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They lined them with a bacteria that\Nrapidly increases cellular aging,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.98,0:05:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,causing anyone who puts their\Nfingers inside to be infected.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why they\Nchose a bowling alley?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Shocker wants to get as many\Nvictims as possible, and quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's return to the\Nlaboratory and investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention, apartment folks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Cockroaches are a\Nplague upon humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all work together to purge\Nthem from our kitchens and houses
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and create a beautiful,\Ncockroach-free apartment complex!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This one-shot cockroach killer\Nis guaranteed effective!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,One spray and the\Ncockroaches are dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.13,0:05:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's only 500 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Come and try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Just 500 yen for all your\Ncockroach-killing needs!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.94,0:05:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't beat that\Nprice, just 500 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, any takers? Any takers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.07,0:05:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.\NThat'll be 500 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:06:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like one, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's buy some, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- Good idea.\N- We'll take one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.50,0:06:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That will be 500 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.02,0:06:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like our\Ncockroach killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.38,0:06:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be trying to interfere\Nwith Shocker's Operation: Cockroach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We made a bundle off that worthless goop.\NYou're something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A real rotten guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your voice down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare to interfere\Nwith Shocker's plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost, Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what's Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.04,0:06:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:07:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a minute! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pay you! Just spare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pay you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You've interfered with\NShocker's Operation: Cockroach.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,As punishment,\NI'll turn you into cockroach men,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.07,0:07:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and put you in charge of\NShocker's germ warfare.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop this! The spray was a scam!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't even work!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.48,0:07:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, spare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin the surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.43,0:08:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Cockroach Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.18,0:08:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, fatty?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.79,0:08:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're next.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.03,0:08:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Spare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll serve Shocker\Nany way you ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.51,0:08:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't make me a cockroach!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pathetic display.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.91,0:08:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll use him as he is, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention,\Nchildren of the apartment complex!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.22,0:08:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We're giving out free\Nballoons, just for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.44,0:08:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, first-come,\Nfirst-served!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on around!\NThey're pretty balloons!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.90,0:08:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.91,0:08:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You came at a great time, Goro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.09,0:08:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.39,0:08:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have a blue one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.55,0:08:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take white!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.68,0:08:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hurry!\N- White, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,White, right?\NYes, here's a white one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.06,0:08:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy was working with\Nthe quack bug spray seller.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:08:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Quack?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.99,0:09:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.86,0:09:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We sprayed that stuff on the\Ncockroaches, but it didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.80,0:09:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what\Nyou're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got the wrong\Nguy, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let him escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You big jerk! You liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Be silent, children!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll make fine guinea pigs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.94,0:09:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Masako, a phone!\NWhere's a phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.84,0:09:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Tachibana...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.18,0:09:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that you, Goro?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, slow down a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What?\NShocker kidnapped children?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Driving north from\NHiraodai Apartment Complex?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood. I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops, tell Taki to join me ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.53,0:10:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He's on our tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... the brat called someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget him. Keep driving!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop! Stop now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.26,0:10:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I'm gonna stop\Njust because you tell me to?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a dead end!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro... I mean, Mr. Cockroach,\Nwhat do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.96,0:10:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Useless trash.\NYou took the wrong road!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:11:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Look... I'm quitting\Nthis rotten line of work!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... spare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.65,0:11:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Please? Spare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.34,0:11:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Traitors must pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.36,0:11:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... so you're the ones\Nspreading the bacteria, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You all right, Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, while you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:12.23,Bumper Episode 53-69,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\pos(280,94)\c&H05008E&}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.61,0:13:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.37,0:13:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hang on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.93,0:13:37.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mysterious illness\Nspreads to anyone who touches
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.57,0:13:39.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,the rapidly aged people as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:42.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and an effective method of\Nfighting it has not yet been found.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:48.82,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(115,488)\c&H462601&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Announcer Yamamoto
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:48.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We'll have more about this incident\Nduring the three o'clock news hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the bacteria-filled\Nad balloon rise
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.86,0:13:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and detonate it in midair\Nto complete the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.68,0:14:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The bacteria will be carried\Non the wind and spread quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.14,0:14:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,causing humans all over\Nto rapidly age and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.59,0:14:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Operation: Ad Balloon will\Ncommence at three o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,See that Hongo and Taki\Nare dealt with before then!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They say the victims\Nwon't last a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.98,0:14:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean...\NThey're going to die like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, after continued aging.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,0:14:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there some\Nmedicine to cure them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing we can\Nmake up in a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we restore this\Nman's consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.51,0:14:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,he might tell us\Nsomething useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.10,0:14:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.12,0:14:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.36,0:15:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,C... Ca...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? Speak up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.58,0:15:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Capsules...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Capsules?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.49,0:15:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In my jacket... jacket...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.37,0:15:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They gave him medicine,\Nto cure him if he was infected!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.73,0:15:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.94,0:15:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The jacket's due to be\Nincinerated to prevent infection!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.57,0:15:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.21,0:16:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw this man out the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.09,0:16:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's coming. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.84,0:16:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course...\NCockroach Man must have done this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.79,0:16:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course... I'll try these.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- I see...\N- Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.53,0:17:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That cockroach\Nbastard ambushed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is what does it, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.13,0:17:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on,\NI'll give you the medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.54,0:17:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.60,0:17:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you know about Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.37,0:17:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,At three o'clock... from the roof\Nof the Sun Building... ad balloon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ad balloon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Release... bacteria...\Nfrom the skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.03,0:18:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.55,0:18:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Look after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one capsule left,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but see if they can analyze\Nand replicate it at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently they're going\Nto release an ad balloon
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,filled with bacteria from\Nthe roof of the Sun Building.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll join you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.25,0:18:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you've had\Na change of heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.80,0:18:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for what I've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an honest man now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.91,0:18:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Just five minutes left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.59,0:18:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.61,0:18:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Cyclone Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.82,0:19:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Preparations complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We've attached the\Nauto-detonator.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, foolish humans...\Nlook up to the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.08,0:19:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now,\NI will kill all of humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.62,0:19:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.28,0:19:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.62,0:20:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.78,0:20:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.86,0:21:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.92,0:21:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Reverse Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:38.91,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.80,0:19:42.26,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:46.45,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:50.00,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:53.71,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:57.25,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:19:59.91,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:03.30,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:07.88,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.88,0:20:11.56,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.66,0:20:22.25,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.25,0:20:24.91,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies made of demons
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.94,0:20:29.43,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten our friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:32.99,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.99,0:20:36.52,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.53,0:20:40.24,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my scarf of red...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.24,0:20:42.77,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.83,0:20:46.65,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:50.95,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:54.67,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.81,0:21:05.48,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.48,0:21:08.62,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies spreading fear
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.98,0:21:12.55,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten our towns,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.55,0:21:16.13,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.13,0:21:19.80,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.81,0:21:23.40,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my mask of green...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.40,0:21:26.42,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.98,0:21:29.60,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.64,0:21:34.26,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.26,0:21:38.03,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.79,0:21:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.\NLet's get to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.21,0:22:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.82,0:22:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We've finished them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.81,0:22:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What a dastardly bunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the medicine finished yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.32,0:22:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo was just heading\Nfor the laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.85,0:22:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.92,0:22:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll be all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.41,0:22:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.01,0:22:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Taki.\NEveryone's waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.82,0:22:57.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And so,\Nthe people's youth returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.84,0:23:02.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But there was no way to restore\Nthe body of cyborg Hongo Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.57,0:23:06.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider's future holds\Nonly endless battles with Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.82,0:23:10.43,Cont,,0,70,150,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.74,0:23:12.68,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.89,0:23:14.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.76,0:23:16.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the monstrous Gireela.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.02,0:23:17.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Gireela spits venomous darts.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.46,0:23:19.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What is Shocker's\NOperation: Poison Water,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.54,0:23:22.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,based around poison capsules\Ncreated from these darts?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.71,0:23:25.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Our Kamen Rider stands\Nagainst their evil plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.09,0:23:26.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week\Nfor more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.82,0:23:30.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "Poison Butterfly of the\NAmazon, Gireela!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.74,0:23:30.72,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fs125\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(517.167,730.389)}Poison Butterfly of the\NAmazon, Gireela
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.55,0:23:40.39,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.97,0:23:42.97,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.97,0:23:44.93,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.93,0:23:47.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.48,0:23:50.35,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.35,0:23:52.23,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.23,0:23:54.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.02,0:23:55.47,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.86,0:23:57.86,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:03.63,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.63,0:24:07.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.16,0:24:10.76,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.24,0:24:15.09,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.81,0:01:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Cockroach Man!!\NThe Dreadful Germ-Stuffed Ad Balloon